{"title":"六月雪","authors":["石春元"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":8,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石春元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳在高天燃烧——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你拈一捧香雪许它一片清冷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见深情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正见深情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少女心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"携一束冰豆花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把炎夏染成熏香纸扇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一扇扇走焦渴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一扇扇走烦闷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用冬的相思铺成玉琢的雪地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你同夏的热恋启开冰雕的心扉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直面过热的夏天——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必定要使心儿冷却"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它才能乍到就怀春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它才能一见便钟情……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}